 {"id":"franken_networkx-axw9","title":"parity: conversion live views should reject update() while frozen","description":"The top-level to_undirected() and to_directed() live views are supposed to be frozen, but update([]) currently succeeds silently in FrankenNetworkX while NetworkX raises NetworkXError('Frozen graph can't be modified'). Preserve the upstream frozen-graph mutation contract for update().","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T07:39:28.936566314Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-21T07:39:28.936566314Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
